{"tid":191852,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"不得不承認鄭俊弘(牙fred)係張學友接班人","createTime":"2017-04-08T07:39:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-09T04:49:01.000Z","uid":52764,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a8185b64b1fc633c30742fada33360cadc36aa96","tid":191852,"uid":52764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T07:39:47.000Z","msg":"以唱功見勝 識作識彈樂器 <br />\n代表作漣漪既一份激情(YEAH YEAH YEAH YEAH) 拍得住學友首李香蘭 <br />\n名曲慢慢地忘掉名字既假音應用 拍得住學友首頭髮亂了 <br />\n經典投降吧 易上口 拍得住學友首每天愛你多一些 <br />\n不得不承認鄭俊弘(牙fred)係張學友接班人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84cb6cab6c2ca71d8090fd90155b639e0e1edc76","tid":191852,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T07:41:46.000Z","msg":"哥哥嘅外表 , 學友嘅唱功 , 發哥嘅演技 , 萬年一遇"},{"pid":"9e450b32eabbe3cfa2e4e2749b35d9edc5be1571","tid":191852,"uid":52764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T07:48:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>哥哥嘅外表 , 學友嘅唱功 , 發哥嘅演技 , 萬年一遇</blockquote><br />\nagger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65c3fef3927de374e9a19995e5b593e7e46eeae2","tid":191852,"uid":52764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T07:50:25.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=m5cPLj0qQ3YL0oTVN36eSjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=800bf332\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】 香港歌手鄭俊弘(Fred)舉行首個個人演唱會《鄭俊弘Welcome to my Dreams 演唱會2014》，獲鍾嘉欣、樂易玲、緋聞女友姜麗文、王君馨、及蔡思貝到場支持，姜麗文亦帶同哥哥姜文杰及父親秦沛支持，可謂總動員出動。而同屬星夢娛樂的藝人吳若希、林師傑、胡鴻鈞、王君馨、姚兵等上台做嘉賓前都坐在台下看表演支持Fred。<br />\nFred首先以自彈自唱結他開場，之後Fred便脫下外套展示訓練多時的二頭肌，在台上大彈結他solo，又似炫耀著他的結他技術！隨後便與自己組的Band合歌，更多謝三位band友:「初初寫歌都是鼓勵自己，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大家一齊堅持就有Rick and roll的精神！</span></strong>」接著與一同參加《星夢傳奇》的鄭世豪及羅鈞滿上台唱歌，羅鈞滿就表示參賽其間都知道Fred非常有實力，更不會忘記一起流過的汗水，而世豪就祝Fred很快使能登上紅館舞台。然後Fred就唱出於《星夢傳奇》的參賽歌《時代曲》，令全場歡呼！<br />\n<br />\n牙FRED的音樂新哲學 - RICK AND ROLL<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b4ba2f3129623b3b26970dc6892ab2e025e3b38","tid":191852,"uid":52764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T04:42:30.000Z","msg":"☺"},{"pid":"39dbc93a960d19a030126cc3ef44f6099580028c","tid":191852,"uid":47250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T04:44:02.000Z","msg":"低質曲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04f0d8faf72a06c37f20981b27b0e55a337bcd68","tid":191852,"uid":52764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T04:49:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>低質曲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真心架"}]}